-Players should make sure ""Enable Diagonal Correction"" is enabled in Flycast's control settings to prevent desyncs","OTG Infinites are not allowed (Mizuki, Gaira, Wan-Fu infinites, etc.) Use of the OTG glitch is permissible for one rep of a combo or for Iroha to combo into her weapon flip.","Nothing needed, just fightcade and OBS",,,N/A,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
