- Leo Black sword is banned so you can use password 11111 11112 for diamond sword instead.",,,,,"1) Tournament will use the ""Easy Password Romhack"" version (search ""redearthep"" on fightcade2). lobby's description has archive.org link, where you can download the romhack file
2) You must set your region for EURO to keep game from desyncing (it may desync if both players are on different regions from one another)
2.1) join the redearthep lobby
2.2) press ""test game""
